name: Mihalism Multi Host
body:
### Welcome
The Mihalism Multi Host mission is to provide the best image hosting software in the world.
Our users know from experience that no hosting script on the Internet comes close to the power that Mihalism Multi Host can provide.
Mihalism Technologies' development team knows that security and compatibility are the most important parts of any software.
Therefore, we have developed advanced features that are compatible with almost any systems. 

### Notice
This page only contains the downloads for the last official versions from Mihalism Technologies.

### Support/Contact
Need some help? Visit http://www.hostmine.us/mihalism & submit a ticket, we'll try to get back to you as soon as possible.
